description:
Spells of Genesis (2015)

The Dragons were the first inhabitants of Askian, invited by the creator himself. They reward the person who brings them their favorite gem, no matter who it is. It is their divine task to trade for a fair price, and make no judgement. Miners from the whole Askian come to Bitkor to sell him their bitcoins.

Supply: 1 of 800

Minted: November 16th 2015
